---
title: Chicken, Roast Cauliflower & Couscous Bowl with Basil Pesto & Herby Mayo
description: Savour the wholesome goodness of this cauliflower couscous bowl, a culinary delight that's good for the body and the soul.
Perfectly roasted veggies sit atop a bed of flavourful Israeli couscous, with a tasty basil pesto mixed through. Topped with herby mayo, this meal is sure to be a favourite!
